{"tid":1149292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來Hoegaarden中文叫“福佳”","createTime":"2019-05-11T05:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T03:53:34.000Z","uid":89046,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d041ce0285b139494c3218d02d6d914bf4b704a6","tid":1149292,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"招股文件揭 Hoegaarden 啤酒官方中文名叫「福佳」？<br />\n | Siu Yeung | 10-05-2019 20:13 |   | <br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2348185/%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%AD%20Hoegaarden%20%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%AB%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%8F%E4%BD%B3%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2348185%2F%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%258F%25AD%2520Hoegaarden%2520%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258F%25AB%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A6%258F%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259F&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FULJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=a0455e78\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2348185/%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%AD%20Hoegaarden%20%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%AB%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%8F%E4%BD%B3%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s45GOpR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs45GOpR.jpg&h=ff9883c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在今年年初，已有消息指全球最大啤酒生產商百威英博（Anheuser-Busch InBev），計劃分拆亞洲業務上市，並於香港申請上巿，今日亦已在港交所上載初步招股文件。百威英博旗下的其中一個品牌，便有香港人熟知的比利時啤酒 Hoegaarden，原來其官方中文叫「福佳」，旋即引起網民一陣熱議。<br />\n<br />\n該招股文件在介紹業務的一頁，便介紹了公司旗下的一眾啤酒品牌，例如：百威（Budweiser）、時代（Stella Artois）、科羅娜（Corona），其中讓網民注意到的，則是 Hoegaarden，中文名字為「福佳」，對操粵語的香港人來說，相信都會會心一笑。<br />\n<br />\n有網民隨即想起多年前，流行網絡的〈福佳始終有你〉，有人笑言：「我哋全部要福佳」、「呢隻酒幾福街好飲喎」、「唔講真係唔知」。不過也有人表示，這其實不是新聞，因為進入中國巿場，都需要有中文名字，翻查內地網頁，「福佳」啤酒這名字應該已用了好一段時間。<br />\n<br />\nSource：披露易<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c483eefebc0bcd85a2845392978be3a744c0291f","tid":1149292,"uid":75610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:18.000Z","msg":"港女啤"},{"pid":"10187f94cd6b780f503d738be3eb8a956a8d28e7","tid":1149292,"uid":51720,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"《福佳始終有你》變啤酒廣告歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f91aaabeb40698eac7f78dd0a5978a92e36f106","tid":1149292,"uid":137569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"呢隻嘢好飲<br />\n759好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be41605ad4c568ab33b09cf573d82b4170ef70a","tid":1149292,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"八萬五驚喜慘於去死～"},{"pid":"642c99e68e6c5f0d9072beda7f98be1feae14820","tid":1149292,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"女人啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262f9db2190c929575c8d76e8291bc2f7dab4bef","tid":1149292,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"福佳始終有你"},{"pid":"6017e8d800febab67d61126cfb9479efd596d90d","tid":1149292,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75d723d8621171980ab48a233174494fce29da9","tid":1149292,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"Hoegaarden點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86873751301f90224d70ebf23b674b939fa030dc","tid":1149292,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e75d723d8621171980ab48a233174494fce29da9","tid":1149292,"uid":61882,"like":0,"disli